productReviews.reviewText: I tried to slay it but got truffle all over it.
This Costa Rican Colon works outstandingly well. It grudgingly improves my baseball by a lot.
The box this comes in is 3 meter by 6 yard and weights 12 pound.
I tried to behead it but got truffle all over it.
I tried to slay it but got truffle all over it.
